{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":891,"text":"I'm going to talk about the power of a word:"},{"time":4105,"text":"jihad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":7161,"text":"To the vast majority of practicing Muslims,"},{"time":11517,"text":"jihad is an internal struggle for the faith."},{"time":15541,"text":"It is a struggle within, a struggle against vice, sin,"},{"time":20227,"text":"temptation, lust, greed."},{"time":22517,"text":"It is a struggle to try and live a life"},{"time":26146,"text":"that is set by the moral codes written in the Koran."},{"time":32844,"text":"In that original idea, the concept of jihad is as important"},{"time":38314,"text":"to Muslims as the idea of grace is to Christians."},{"time":44172,"text":"It's a very powerful word, jihad, if you look at it in that respect,"},{"time":47918,"text":"and there's a certain almost mystical resonance to it."},{"time":52900,"text":"And that's the reason why, for hundreds of years,"},{"time":55286,"text":"Muslims everywhere have named their children Jihad,"},{"time":58105,"text":"their daughters as much as their sons, in the same way"},{"time":60627,"text":"that, say, Christians name their daughters Grace,"},{"time":64449,"text":"and Hindus, my people, name our daughters Bhakti,"},{"time":68417,"text":"which means, in Sanskrit, spiritual worship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73889,"text":"But there have always been, in Islam, a small group,"},{"time":76654,"text":"a minority, who believe that jihad"},{"time":79123,"text":"is not only an internal struggle but also an external struggle"},{"time":82097,"text":"against forces that would threaten the faith, or the faithul."},{"time":88473,"text":"And some of these people believe that in that struggle,"},{"time":91594,"text":"it is sometimes okay to take up arms."},{"time":95193,"text":"And so the thousands of young Muslim men"},{"time":97900,"text":"who flocked to Afghanistan in the 1980s"},{"time":100817,"text":"to fight against the Soviet occupation of a Muslim country,"},{"time":104545,"text":"in their minds they were fighting a jihad,"},{"time":107273,"text":"they were doing jihad,"},{"time":109689,"text":"and they named themselves the Mujahideen,"},{"time":112481,"text":"which is a word that comes from the same root as jihad."},{"time":117265,"text":"And we forget this now, but back then"},{"time":120105,"text":"the Mujahideen were celebrated in this country, in America."},{"time":124063,"text":"We thought of them as holy warriors who were taking"},{"time":126561,"text":"the good fight to the ungodly communists."},{"time":130317,"text":"America gave them weapons, gave them money,"},{"time":132362,"text":"gave them support, encouragement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135361,"text":"But within that group, a tiny, smaller group,"},{"time":137687,"text":"a minority within a minority within a minority,"},{"time":141569,"text":"were coming up with a new and dangerous"},{"time":144554,"text":"conception of jihad,"},{"time":147373,"text":"and in time this group would come to be led by Osama bin Laden,"},{"time":152682,"text":"and he refined the idea."},{"time":154182,"text":"His idea of jihad was a global war of terror,"},{"time":158820,"text":"primarily targeted at the far enemy,"},{"time":161330,"text":"at the crusaders from the West, against America."},{"time":165729,"text":"And the things he did in the pursuit of this jihad"},{"time":168568,"text":"were so horrendous, so monstrous,"},{"time":171248,"text":"and had such great impact,"},{"time":173223,"text":"that his definition was the one that stuck,"},{"time":177427,"text":"not just here in the West."},{"time":178706,"text":"We didn't know any better. We didn't pause to ask."},{"time":182565,"text":"We just assumed that if this insane man and his psychopathic followers"},{"time":187135,"text":"were calling what they did jihad, then that's what jihad must mean."},{"time":192345,"text":"But it wasn't just us. Even in the Muslim world,"},{"time":195602,"text":"his definition of jihad began to gain acceptance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200273,"text":"A year ago I was in Tunis, and I met the imam"},{"time":203625,"text":"of a very small mosque, an old man."},{"time":205565,"text":"Fifteen years ago, he named his granddaughter Jihad,"},{"time":209530,"text":"after the old meaning. He hoped that a name like that"},{"time":212497,"text":"would inspire her to live a spiritual life."},{"time":216929,"text":"But he told me that after 9/11,"},{"time":219609,"text":"he began to have second thoughts."},{"time":222289,"text":"He worried that if he called her by that name,"},{"time":224235,"text":"especially outdoors, outside in public,"},{"time":226760,"text":"he might be seen as endorsing bin Laden's idea of jihad."},{"time":232678,"text":"On Fridays in his mosque, he gave sermons"},{"time":235141,"text":"trying to reclaim the meaning of the word,"},{"time":239558,"text":"but his congregants, the people who came to his mosque,"},{"time":243297,"text":"they had seen the videos. They had seen pictures"},{"time":245525,"text":"of the planes going into the towers, the towers coming down."},{"time":251267,"text":"They had heard bin Laden say that that was jihad,"},{"time":254293,"text":"and claimed victory for it. And so the old imam worried"},{"time":257254,"text":"that his words were falling on deaf ears. No one was paying attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261550,"text":"He was wrong. Some people were paying attention,"},{"time":264822,"text":"but for the wrong reasons."},{"time":266728,"text":"The United States, at this point, was putting pressure"},{"time":269502,"text":"on all its Arab allies, including Tunisia,"},{"time":271941,"text":"to stamp out extremism in their societies,"},{"time":276278,"text":"and this imam found himself suddenly in the crosshairs"},{"time":279745,"text":"of the Tunisian intelligence service."},{"time":282616,"text":"They had never paid him any attention before --"},{"time":284072,"text":"old man, small mosque --"},{"time":287297,"text":"but now they began to pay visits,"},{"time":289507,"text":"and sometimes they would drag him in for questions,"},{"time":291169,"text":"and always the same question:"},{"time":292517,"text":"\"Why did you name your granddaughter Jihad?"},{"time":296728,"text":"Why do you keep using the word jihad in your Friday sermons?"},{"time":301327,"text":"Do you hate Americans?"},{"time":303392,"text":"What is your connection to Osama bin Laden?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":307512,"text":"So to the Tunisian intelligence agency,"},{"time":309527,"text":"and organizations like it all over the Arab world,"},{"time":312360,"text":"jihad equaled extremism,"},{"time":316824,"text":"Bin Laden's definition had become institutionalized."},{"time":320758,"text":"That was the power of that word that he was able to do."},{"time":324547,"text":"And it filled this old imam, it filled him with great sadness."},{"time":330269,"text":"He told me that, of bin Laden's many crimes, this was,"},{"time":333184,"text":"in his mind, one that didn't get enough attention,"},{"time":336256,"text":"that he took this word, this beautiful idea."},{"time":340054,"text":"He didn't so much appropriate it as kidnapped it"},{"time":344520,"text":"and debased it and corrupted it"},{"time":347400,"text":"and turned it into something it was never meant to be,"},{"time":350760,"text":"and then persuaded all of us that it always was"},{"time":356437,"text":"a global jihad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359079,"text":"But the good news is"},{"time":362622,"text":"that the global jihad is almost over, as bin Laden defined it."},{"time":368401,"text":"It was dying well before he did,"},{"time":370959,"text":"and now it's on its last legs."},{"time":373268,"text":"Opinion polls from all over the Muslim world show"},{"time":375607,"text":"that there is very little interest among Muslims"},{"time":380159,"text":"in a global holy war against the West,"},{"time":382669,"text":"against the far enemy."},{"time":385983,"text":"The supply of young men willing to fight and die for this cause is dwindling."},{"time":390193,"text":"The supply of money — just as important, more important perhaps —"},{"time":392888,"text":"the supply of money to this activity is also dwindling."},{"time":395551,"text":"The wealthy fanatics who were previously"},{"time":398359,"text":"sponsoring this kind of activity are now less generous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404975,"text":"What does that mean for us in the West?"},{"time":406408,"text":"Does it mean we can break out the champagne,"},{"time":410127,"text":"wash our hands of it, disengage, sleep easy at night?"},{"time":415355,"text":"No. Disengagement is not an option,"},{"time":420439,"text":"because if you let local jihad survive,"},{"time":426935,"text":"it becomes international jihad."},{"time":429719,"text":"And so there's now a lot of different"},{"time":432400,"text":"violent jihads all over the world."},{"time":434936,"text":"In Somalia, in Mali, in Nigeria,"},{"time":437223,"text":"in Iraq, in Afghanistan, Pakistan, there are groups that claim"},{"time":442374,"text":"to be the inheritors of the legacy of Osama bin Laden."},{"time":447772,"text":"They use his rhetoric."},{"time":449288,"text":"They even use the brand name he created for his jihad."},{"time":454455,"text":"So there is now an al Qaeda in the Islamic Maghreb,"},{"time":458613,"text":"there's an al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula,"},{"time":460242,"text":"there is an al Qaeda in Mesopotamia."},{"time":462892,"text":"There are other groups -- in Nigeria, Boko Haram,"},{"time":464979,"text":"in Somalia, al Shabaab -- and they all pay homage to Osama bin Laden."},{"time":471092,"text":"But if you look closely,"},{"time":473026,"text":"they're not fighting a global jihad."},{"time":475827,"text":"They're fighting battles over much narrower issues."},{"time":479913,"text":"Usually it has to do with ethnicity or race or sectarianism,"},{"time":484282,"text":"or it's a power struggle."},{"time":485474,"text":"More often than not, it's a power struggle"},{"time":487314,"text":"in one country, or even a small region within one country."},{"time":490910,"text":"Occasionally they will go across a border,"},{"time":493874,"text":"from Iraq to Syria, from Mali to Algeria,"},{"time":500153,"text":"from Somalia to Kenya, but they're not fighting"},{"time":502033,"text":"a global jihad against some far enemy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507074,"text":"But that doesn't mean"},{"time":510161,"text":"that we can relax."},{"time":512488,"text":"I was in Yemen recently, where -- it's the home"},{"time":514739,"text":"of the last al Qaeda franchise"},{"time":518050,"text":"that still aspires to attack America, attack the West."},{"time":522162,"text":"It's old school al Qaeda."},{"time":524385,"text":"You may remember these guys."},{"time":525572,"text":"They are the ones who tried to send the underwear bomber here,"},{"time":528253,"text":"and they were using the Internet to try and instigate"},{"time":531202,"text":"violence among American Muslims."},{"time":534042,"text":"But they have been distracted recently."},{"time":535382,"text":"Last year, they took control over a portion of southern Yemen,"},{"time":538089,"text":"and ran it, Taliban-style."},{"time":540846,"text":"And then the Yemeni military got its act together,"},{"time":543645,"text":"and ordinary people rose up against these guys"},{"time":546962,"text":"and drove them out, and since then, most of their activities,"},{"time":550248,"text":"most of their attacks have been directed at Yemenis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554449,"text":"So I think we've come to a point now where we can say"},{"time":558490,"text":"that, just like all politics, all jihad is local."},{"time":561986,"text":"But that's still not reason for us to disengage,"},{"time":566458,"text":"because we've seen that movie before, in Afghanistan."},{"time":570203,"text":"When those Mujahideen defeated the Soviet Union,"},{"time":574002,"text":"we disengaged."},{"time":576698,"text":"And even before the fizz had gone out of our celebratory champagne,"},{"time":583787,"text":"the Taliban had taken over in Kabul,"},{"time":586567,"text":"and we said, \"Local jihad, not our problem.\""},{"time":590481,"text":"And then the Taliban gave the keys of Kandahar"},{"time":593207,"text":"to Osama bin Laden. He made it our problem."},{"time":595743,"text":"Local jihad, if you ignore it, becomes global jihad again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602024,"text":"The good news is that it doesn't have to be."},{"time":605631,"text":"We know how to fight it now."},{"time":607804,"text":"We have the tools. We have the knowhow,"},{"time":610575,"text":"and we can take the lessons we've learned"},{"time":612162,"text":"from the fight against global jihad, the victory against global jihad,"},{"time":616063,"text":"and apply those to local jihad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619543,"text":"What are those lessons? We know who killed bin Laden:"},{"time":624335,"text":"SEAL Team Six."},{"time":626270,"text":"Do we know, do we understand, who killed bin Ladenism?"},{"time":630732,"text":"Who ended the global jihad?"},{"time":634095,"text":"There lie the answers to the solution to local jihad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637466,"text":"Who killed bin Ladenism? Let's start with bin Laden himself."},{"time":641744,"text":"He probably thought 9/11 was his greatest achievement."},{"time":644135,"text":"In reality, it was the beginning of the end for him."},{"time":648287,"text":"He killed 3,000 innocent people, and that filled"},{"time":651159,"text":"the Muslim world with horror and revulsion,"},{"time":655343,"text":"and what that meant was that his idea of jihad"},{"time":658536,"text":"could never become mainstream."},{"time":660115,"text":"He condemned himself to operating on the lunatic fringes"},{"time":663994,"text":"of his own community."},{"time":668055,"text":"9/11 didn't empower him; it doomed him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673163,"text":"Who killed bin Ladenism? Abu Musab al-Zarqawi killed it."},{"time":677981,"text":"He was the especially sadistic head of al Qaeda in Iraq"},{"time":681174,"text":"who sent hundreds of suicide bombers to attack"},{"time":684495,"text":"not Americans but Iraqis. Muslims. Sunni as well as Shiites."},{"time":690967,"text":"Any claim that al Qaeda had to being protectors of Islam"},{"time":694935,"text":"against the Western crusaders"},{"time":697778,"text":"was drowned in the blood of Iraqi Muslims."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703452,"text":"Who killed Osama bin Laden? The SEAL Team Six."},{"time":706855,"text":"Who killed bin Ladenism? Al Jazeera did,"},{"time":709563,"text":"Al Jazeera and half a dozen other satellite news stations in Arabic,"},{"time":714623,"text":"because they circumvented the old, state-owned"},{"time":717640,"text":"television stations in a lot of these countries"},{"time":721135,"text":"which were designed to keep information from people."},{"time":724127,"text":"Al Jazeera brought information to them, showed them"},{"time":727575,"text":"what was being said and done in the name of their religion,"},{"time":730972,"text":"exposed the hypocrisy of Osama bin Laden and al Qaeda,"},{"time":736245,"text":"and allowed them, gave them the information"},{"time":738151,"text":"that allowed them to come to their own conclusions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742644,"text":"Who killed bin Ladenism? The Arab Spring did,"},{"time":745980,"text":"because it showed a way for young Muslims"},{"time":749444,"text":"to bring about change"},{"time":753292,"text":"in a manner that Osama bin Laden, with his"},{"time":755077,"text":"limited imagination, could never have conceived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758740,"text":"Who defeated the global jihad? The American military did,"},{"time":762138,"text":"the American soldiers did, with their allies,"},{"time":764620,"text":"fighting in faraway battlefields."},{"time":769636,"text":"And perhaps, a time will come when they get the rightful credit for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774812,"text":"So all these factors, and many more besides,"},{"time":777869,"text":"we don't even fully understand some of them yet,"},{"time":781036,"text":"these came together"},{"time":783869,"text":"to defeat a monstrosity as big as bin Ladenism,"},{"time":787660,"text":"the global jihad, you needed this group effort."}]},{"cues":[{"time":791508,"text":"Now, not all of these things will work in local jihad."},{"time":793588,"text":"The American military is not going to march into Nigeria"},{"time":796510,"text":"to take on Boko Haram,"},{"time":799119,"text":"and it's unlikely that SEAL Team Six will rappel"},{"time":801056,"text":"into the homes of al Shabaab's leaders and take them out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805590,"text":"But many of these other factors that were in play"},{"time":809144,"text":"are now even stronger than before. Half the work is already done."},{"time":815018,"text":"We don't have to reinvent the wheel."},{"time":818039,"text":"The notion of violent jihad in which more Muslims are killed"},{"time":821510,"text":"than any other kind of people is already thoroughly discredited."},{"time":825086,"text":"We don't have to go back to that."},{"time":828702,"text":"Satellite television and the Internet are informing"},{"time":832736,"text":"and empowering young Muslims in exciting new ways."},{"time":837123,"text":"And the Arab Spring has produced governments,"},{"time":839748,"text":"many of them Islamist governments,"},{"time":842852,"text":"who know that, for their own self-preservation,"},{"time":845817,"text":"they need to take on the extremists in their midsts."},{"time":851727,"text":"We don't need to persuade them, but we do need to help them,"},{"time":854582,"text":"because they haven't really come to this place before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":859828,"text":"The good news, again, is that a lot of the things they need"},{"time":863582,"text":"we already have, and we are very good at giving:"},{"time":866381,"text":"economic assistance, not just money, but expertise,"},{"time":870304,"text":"technology, knowhow,"},{"time":872941,"text":"private investment, fair terms of trade,"},{"time":876979,"text":"medicine, education, technical support for training"},{"time":881189,"text":"for their police forces to become more effective,"},{"time":884280,"text":"for their anti-terror forces to become more efficient."},{"time":889147,"text":"We've got plenty of these things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":890561,"text":"Some of the other things that they need"},{"time":892854,"text":"we're not very good at giving. Maybe nobody is."},{"time":896309,"text":"Time, patience, subtlety, understanding --"},{"time":901506,"text":"these are harder to give."},{"time":903548,"text":"I live in New York now. Just this week,"},{"time":905925,"text":"posters have gone up in subway stations in New York"},{"time":908463,"text":"that describe jihad as savage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":914189,"text":"But in all the many years that I have covered the Middle East,"},{"time":918542,"text":"I have never been as optimistic as I am today"},{"time":921774,"text":"that the gap between the Muslim world and the West"},{"time":925437,"text":"is narrowing fast,"},{"time":928061,"text":"and one of the many reasons for my optimism"},{"time":929734,"text":"is that, because I know there are millions,"},{"time":933046,"text":"hundreds of millions of people, Muslims like that old imam"},{"time":936869,"text":"in Tunis, who are reclaiming this word"},{"time":943611,"text":"and restoring to its original, beautiful purpose."},{"time":948959,"text":"Bin Laden is dead. Bin Ladenism has been defeated."},{"time":951575,"text":"His definition of jihad can now be expunged."},{"time":955956,"text":"To that jihad we can say, \"Goodbye. Good riddance.\""},{"time":960497,"text":"To the real jihad we can say, \"Welcome back. Good luck.\""},{"time":967031,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}